Sentiment Analysis Using Azure Text Analytics

ðŸ’¬ Overview
The Text Analytics API provides NLP features such as sentiment analysis, key phrase extraction, and language detection.

Program:
from azure.ai.textanalytics import TextAnalyticsClient, AzureKeyCredential

endpoint = "https://centralindia.api.cognitive.microsoft.com/"
key = "9VZbnCZ0CCm4xYTKTslmLzPKe588visu9MWrqofpGRSphcgRDhchJQQJ99BKACGhslBXJ3w3AAAYACOGIxSE"

client = TextAnalyticsClient(endpoint=endpoint, credential=AzureKeyCredential(key))

documents = ["I love using Azure AI services!"]
response = client.analyze_sentiment(documents=documents)[0]
print(f"Sentiment: {response.sentiment}, Score: {response.confidence_scores}")
